profile:
Green Side Up Contracting Inc. is a professional member of Landscape Ontario & we are an authorized TrexPro - Platinum status!

Over the last 22 years, we have established ourselves within the construction industry as an honest and reputable contractor.  We have earned this reputation by shaping the company around four core values: honesty, transparency, quality of workmanship, backed by above industry-standard warranties!

As the President of Green Side Up Contracting Inc. and a board member of the Toronto Chapter of Landscape Ontario, PROTECTING YOUR INVESTMENT and delivering EXCELLENCE are two of Jay's key priorities.

         ****************************10 YEAR STRUCTURAL WARRANTY - FENCING ****************************

Green Side Up Contracting Inc is a consistent award-winning, construction company that focuses on delivering high-quality workmanship and superior customer service.  We put our trust into our clients with extremely favorable payment terms - pay when the job is completed! We are active members of our community and believe in helping those who are less fortunate.

Services provided include but are not limited to:

-> Fence Construction (80' linear feet minumum)
 
-> Interlocking & Landscape Construction

-> Deck Construction (200 sq foot minumim) 

    - Trex
    - Cedar

***

Not only does Green Side Up Contracting Inc focus on PROTECTING YOUR INVESTMENT by offering a TEN-YEAR structural WARRANTY on fencing, we also believe that doing business together should be simple and transparent.

***

Please use our SELF SERVE CALCULATORS to obtain an INSTANT ESTIMATE for your DECK, FENCE or INTERLOCK project:

FENCE CALCULATOR: https://greensideupcontracting.com/fence-building-calculator/

DECK CALCULATOR: https://greensideupcontracting.com/deck-calculator/

INTERLOCKING CALCULATOR: https://greensideupcontracting.com/interlock-cost-calculator/

***

Please be sure to check our work by visiting:

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/greensideupcontracting/

YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCRNuc7PofUOEHCwMf7NdUzQ/videos?view_as=subscriber

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/GreenSideUpContracting/

We would also invite you to come on site during the construction process, so you can see our work in progress!

***

Building is fun, business is great, people are terrific and life is wonderful! 

I ask that you put your trust into Green Side Up Contracting - we not disappoint!!

On your side,

Jay Saveall

www.greensideupcontracting.com

profile:
We are Action Home Services, and we always take action for every construction service that you need. Based in Toronto, Ontario, we are a general contracting company that specializes in a wide range of services. We will help you to design and build an outside living area of your dream. Do not wait! Take action with Action Home Services. Check our website at http://actionhomeservices.ca/ to find out more. 

Our Mission
We aim to become one of the most successful construction companies within Toronto, Ontario. This mission will not happen if our services are not up to the level of what our customers are expecting. Thus our main aim is to provide the best services to our customers. Our level of professionalism will become our barometer for customer satisfaction. We also aim to make it a point to have strong ties with our customers so we can grow the level of our professionalism and gain more trust among our clients.

Our Vision
Our dream is to become the one-stop shop for any kind of construction service that any of our clients need. We initially started with interlocking and asphalt paving, but we are now venturing into other services such as landscaping, pressure washing and sealing, concreting, decks and fences, demolition services and many more. We already have a wide range of service offerings, but we are not satisfied with just these. We are excited about every project that we perform and our possibilities for improvement and additional services are endless.

Our Commitment 
We commit to do whatever it takes to achieve the level of satisfaction our customer deserves. Our workmanship will leave a lasting mark and one that will be a reminder of our professionalism and close ties with our clients. We gained the trust of our customers through hard work that pays off when we see our clients happy with the outcome of our services. We will strive to be cooperative and readily available for any queries or requests our customer needs.

profile:
M.E. Contracting is one of Toronto's premier outdoor solutions companies. 

M.E. was Founded by owners Keren and Eitan Abu, with a desire to change the face of Toronto through the revitalization of outdoor living space. The “M” and “E” stand for Keren and Eitan's daughters, Mika and Emma. From the start these two girls have inspired the vision of innovation and creativity that M.E. embodies today. 

Specializing in custom landscape design, M.E. Contracting has spent over a decade executing this vision of innovation and construction. From decking to interlocking tile and pool building, M.E. Contracting differs from other Toronto landscapers through our commitment to excellence and attention to even the smallest of details. 

Want to see for yourself? Our 7,000 square foot landscaping showroom is the only showroom in Ontario dedicated to landscaping and outdoor transformations. Our exquisite showroom encapsulates features of all the custom design elements that every home owner dreams of having in their outdoor home space. In addition to the amazing  materials we have on display, our showroom includes an in-ground swimming pool with waterfalls, outdoor kitchens and outdoor furniture for prospective clients to experience.

Our vast experience in all aspects of landscaping design and construction has provided us with the ability to take on an array of projects, both varying in shape and size. Now matter what our goal to produce astounding and exceptional work remains unchanging. We aim to go above and beyond in our passion for what we do, and as a result we aim to surpass our client’s expectations with each and every element of landscaping design.

profile:
Canada’s Gardenland is a leading domestic landscape construction and maintenance service provider in the Greater Toronto area. Our team of lawn specialists utilizes their knowledge of lawn science and their skills of artistic application to create the perfect look for your specific landscaping scenario. We understand that each property and client taste is different so we work diligently with you and your surroundings to tailor the best approach for meeting those needs. Canada’s Gardenland has both the tools and the experience available to help you bring your landscaping dream to life.
Canada’s Gardenland designs, creates, maintains and provides tools for domestic landscaping projects in the Greater Toronto area. Both artistic landscaping skills and applied lawn science is utilized in order to achieve the perfect atmosphere and our professional team works closely with clients to ensure that projects meet specific needs and requirements.

Proper landscaping requires the application of various aspects in order to make your property look its best. Therefore, Canada’s Gardenland first helps with the design and creation of the right landscaping techniques that complement the natural lay of land as well as any man-made structures on the premises. We also offer a variety of interlocking stone techniques that provide landscaping accents through beautifully designed and applied walkways, driveways and patios.

We can also apply creative outdoor lighting effects so that your landscape is transformed into a stunning sight of beauty after dark and provides safety to those visiting after hours. Quality landscaping maintenance is also offered through sod fertilization, trimming, grooming, replanting and cleaning so that your property always looks its best.

profile:
Pro-Loc Interlocking & Landscape Design is a privately owned company established in 2003. 
With an early focus on residential interlocking and landscaping contracts, Pro-Loc has matured into a full service residential and commercial interlocking company with expertise spanning all aspects of large-scale project disciplines.

profile:
Singular Focus:

Most landscape and renovation companies try to serve many types of customers at the same time; homeowners, shopping centers, office buildings, golf courses, and the list goes on. They are pulled in all directions trying to be everything to everyone. At Captain Handy Co, we focus on one customer, you, the homeowner. We have a singular focus on bringing you the best landscaping and interior renovation, the best customer service, and the best value for your home. When you consider that quality renovation can improve the value of your home by 10%-15%, why wouldn’t you hire the one company that focuses specifically on residential landscaping? We are Your Residential Landscape and interior renovation Company.
Easy:

Our business makes your life easier. We are committed to improving the quality of life for our customers so they can spend their time on other things. Our customers are busy and have hectic lives. They do not have time to deal with different companies for lawn care, mowing, design, patio building. Captain Handy Co. offers turn-key solutions to your landscape needs. One call connects you with one of our very qualified Landscape Advisors who will make sure that you are delighted with your landscape. It is that easy.
Hassle-Free:

Ever notice how some companies make it a hassle just to do business with them? Who needs hassles? Life is complicated enough as it is. With Captain Handy Co, you can expect fast response times, clear and concise proposals, and work to be done how and when we promise it would be. You can also expect us to stand behind our work, show up when we say we will and take care of the little things that can take a landscape,renovation and experience, from blah to wow! We take away the hassles so all you have to do is enjoy your landscape.
Professional:

With 5 years under our belts, we know a thing or two about being the professional contractor of choice. Our staff has an average tenure rate of over twelve years, and some team members have been with us for over two decades! They undergo extensive and on-going training to not only assure that your renovation looks fantastic, but also to make sure that you are treated superbly. Our staff members are clearly recognizable in their sharp uniforms so you will know who is on your property. With so many companies claiming to be “professional”, isn’t it nice to work with a company that actually is?
Our Values:

At Captain Handy Co, we provide Tender Loving Care to both you and your interior and landscape renovation. These are our Values:
•	Treat people honestly, fairly and with respect in all situations
•	Create a comfortable environment in which to work and do business
•	Be open to problems and complaints, and work quickly to a fair resolution
•	Present a professional image and working safely
•	Have a “can-do” attitude
•	Stand behind our commitment to quality and service
•	Be active, responsible and positive citizens in the communities in which we work

profile:
Mr. Interlock Landscape & Construction is a professional residential and commercial design and build firm servicing the York Region and Greater Toronto Area communities.
 
With over 30 years of experience in interlocking and paving installations, we help our clients create a distinctive design element that will magnify their homes allure, increase its value while offering a unique look customized to meet their landscape desires.
 
We take pride in providing our clients with original and timeless designs, innovative ideas, quality construction, prompt and professional service, outstanding warranty and seamless flow of project implementation from start to finish.
 
Our construction expertise spans across a variety of materials from natural stone, flagstone, marble to cobblestones, standard pavers, concrete and asphalt.
 
We also specialize in a variety of project types such as driveways, patios, stairs, retaining walls, swimming pools, outdoor kitchenettes, outdoor living spaces, outdoor lighting, outdoor audio and more.
 
Our mission is to enhance and beautify the communities we enter by supplying our clients with a uniquely designed landscape project that adheres to our motto "Do It Once, Do It Right". All while providing our clients with unparalleled service through our consultation, planning and execution resulting in long lasting relationships and an abundance of word of mouth referrals.

profile:
Winner of many awards including a national and provincial award for best residential design. With passion and creativity and over twenty years' experience in beautifying properties all over the GTA, Land-Con prides itself on customer satisfaction and customer experience before, during and after the project is completed. We are very honest with our customers, keeping them up to date regularly with the progress of the project. We strive to give our customers the highest quality of work, starting with our very experienced in house, award winning landscape designers, as well as extremely professional and respectable trade personal on the job site, with the owners them selves over seeing every single project on a daily basis.
We have received industry wide recognition for design and build, professionalism and customer satisfaction.


ACCOMPLISHED TEAM
Active Member of Landscape Ontario and Bild.  ICPI and NCMA certified.  Techno-Bloc Pro installer.  Permacon Pro installer.  2016 Winner of 2 Landscape Awards of Excellence, 2017 winner of 3 landscape awards of excellence, 2019 National Award, 2020 Winner of 3 landscape awards of excellence and the Van Casey award for best Design. 
At Land-Con, our principles, passion and reputation speak for themselves.  Our valued clients will agree; excellence in project management, coupled with our highly qualified management and crew are second to none.


COMPASSIONATE CARE
We build to capture and reflect the unique vision our clients trust us to create while abiding to strict standards and timelines.  We value your expectations and opinion and respect the importance of budget guidelines.  The job site will always be left cleaned up and tidy and ready for next day construction.  We respect your property and will be courteous and considerate of you and your neighbors.


AFTER CARE
At Land-con we believe that after a project is completed the aftercare with our customers is just as important as any part of the project.  If at any time after the project is completed, you have any questions or concerns we are here to help.  We back our workmanship with a five year extended warranty.  This warranty is transferable if you happen to sell your home within the five year period.  Our top priority is customer service.  We take pride in providing courteous prompt responses to all clients past and current.

ABOUT THE OWNERS

Growing up together for the past 30 years, Ofer Winkler and Jeremy Lerner have formed a strong friendship which naturally became a great partnership.  They have both been in the landscape industry since 1997 giving each of them over 20 years experience in this industry.  Each one brings to the table their specialized onsite experience, and combined with their in class courses that they have attended over the years, makes them a team like no other.  Ofer and Jeremy have a passion for the landscape industry and each project they built over the years, which gives each home owner their own unique experience.  Their mission and vision is to give every home owner and project they build the attention and time they deserve.  This has made Land-Con a well-respected company by home owners, suppliers and even competitors around the GTA.  Together, they are an award winning team that transforms their clients' vision into reality, while providing professional services that meet the budget and time line.

profile:
Since we started serving the GTA in 2006 we have been dedicated to providing the ultimate finished product. We specialize in residential and commercial landscaping including Re/Re work such as trench and boulevard restoration. All of our work is designed to not only be aesthetically pleasing but also withstand the harsh Canadian climate. We also provide a complete property maintenance service for condo complexes, plazas, and residential. The end goal is to provide the best quality service to our clients. 

All jobs are fully insured and bonded. 

**

We provide helpful suggestions and create beautiful custom designs suitable for any budget. The sales representative's job isn't over after the contract is signed, they are there to help throughout the process, ready to answer any questions you might have and handle changes at the customers request in a professional and timely manner. Daily updates on how the project is going are provided to ensure that everything has been completed to our customers needs. We warranty all of our work. Our plan is to make sure that all of our customers enjoy working with us and enjoy their new outdoor space. 

**

Please contact us and we would be happy to send a sales representative out for a free quote with no obligation.

profile: Royal Stone is a recognized installer of premier interlocking paving stones, retaining walls, steps, curbs, and natural stone products. Whether you're designing a complete streetscape or a residential walkway, patio and driveway, Royal Stone can provide you with a range of applications. Our qualified staff will take your project from the design stage to completion in an organized and professional manner. Let your surroundings express who you are. Royal Stone's experienced landscape designers will guide you in selecting features that come together to create balance and harmony. Our use of hand drawn and computer-generated renderings effectively bridge the gap between concept and reality, assuring our clients that their new surroundsing will be all that they envisioned - and more. DRIVEWAYS / WALKWAYS Driveways and walkways provide curb appearl to homes. They are a point of artistic expression allowing customers to express their personal style. OUTDOOR LIVING Outdoor living spaces provide an impressive focal point where you can relax, dine and entertain with familiy and friends. Outdoor kitchens, fireplaces and firepits are just some of the possibilities. POOLS Pools provide an impressive focal point where you can relax and entertain with family and friends. Spas are great alternative for spaces wehre a pool is not feasible. WE SPECIALIZE IN Driveways, Walkways, Interlocking Stone, Flagstone, Pools, Spas, Hot Tubs, Water Features, Inifinity Edge, Landscaping, Patios, Cabanas, Gazebos, Outdoor Kitchens & Fireplaces

profile: In 2007, Green FX Landscaping was founded by Pino and Rob Arpa and began services the following spring. Since then, Green FX Landscaping has continued to provide exceptional, complete lawn maintenance for residential and commercial properties.  The knowledgeable technicians at Green FX Landscaping are made up of passionate people, each having years of experience in lawn and garden maintenance, new lawn installation (hydro seeding, terraseeding and sodding), and landscape management.  Building long-lasting and trusting relationships with our customers is very important to us and we strive to provide our clients with exceptional customer service and satisfaction. We take the time to get to know each of our clients so that we can better understand their vision and goals for their project to provide stunning results!  At Green FX Landscaping, your landscape is not only a representation of you but it is also a reflection of us; so you can take comfort in the fact that pride, precision, and hard work goes into every project.  Whether your property needs are residential or commercial, we will work with you to create the perfect lawn treatment plan that compliments your style and budget while protecting your investment and preserving the environment.

profile:
Design Turf has a 20-year history of selling ProGreen artificial grass products in the GTA and beyond. Our residential grass series has a brown fiber thatch producing a realistic looking grass and is 33% cooler than conventional turf. Plus, with the new patent-pending ProFlow backing that increases the drainage rate by approximately 400% and our moisture resistant fibers, the turf will be cleaner, drier and free from any unpleasant pet odors. Design Turf is also recognized for offering the highest quality of golf green products & for their professional installations. Design Turf golf greens are priced at $30/ft²+HST for full installation. A small 12’x15’, 2 hole backyard golf green can be as little as $7500+HST complete! 
 
Our most popular selling landscape turf averages $19/ft²+HST for full installation. All our turf is pet friendly and has excellent drainage! 
 
ProGreen manufacturing is the only North American artificial grass manufacturer to produce their products under one roof from start to finish. Our products are certifiably 100% LEAD & HEAVY METAL FREE!  ProGreen products have a life expectancy of 30-40 years, even under the harshest of conditions, including the play of multiple dogs or when used by busy daycare centers!
 
For the Do-It-Yourselfer
Design Turf’s price on Natural Prime 50 for supply only is just $6.20/ft²+HST (remember it supplied only and the rolls are 15' wide!). Find out how to install it yourself here!
 
Please contact us! Provide a daytime phone number, email address and street address, we ’ll be happy to show you samples and arrange a free quotation.

profile:
Bestloc Interlocking is trusted and respected landscape design and Installation company operating in the Greater Toronto and Surrounding Areas. As a proud and certified member of ICPI (Interlocking and Concrete Pavement Institute), we provide our clients with award winning landscape designs and industry leading installations. Bestloc was found on two main principles of encouraging family outdoor living and building structures that last.

Many years ago, Ryan Morant, founder and president started out being a labourer, where he developed his passion for the trade. He then became a foreman, and inspector, and subsequently a teacher. Under his leadership, our professional team of highly skilled and qualified personnel provides innovative landscape designs. With over 15 years of planting and masonry experience, and hundreds of thousands of square feet laid, Bestloc Interlocking embodies the values of strength, performance, and passion. We are dedicated to providing our clients with custom landscaping solutions.

We are in constant communication with our friends at ICPI (Interlocking and Concrete Pavement Institute), and are always up-to-date on industry leading techniques on landscape designs and installations. We offer good communication with our clients from the beginning of each project to its completion. Our experienced project management means your project is completed on time and on budget.

Furthermore, we complete every task with a commitment to integrity and a devotion to excellence using the best quality products guaranteed to leave a lasting impression. If you wish to create the finest outdoor living experience for you and your family, please do not hesitate to contact Bestloc Interlocking for a free consultation/estimate.

profile:
We started our Landscape and Interlocking Stone business in 1994 based on three pillars:  Integrity, Quality, and Service.

ONE job at a time… Unlike many other businesses we do ONE job at a time. It is important to us to be able to focus all our efforts into each customer so that they get the best in personal attention and their project is completed as expected and on time.

No Sub-Contracted Work…   We do all the work ourselves. Our employees are highly qualified, talented, and honest. We wouldn’t trust your project and our reputation to anyone else.

We deliver what we promise to do. We carry out our work according to what our customers want and expect. We strive to deliver the best results at the least possible cost for the client.
Our work exceeds construction standards and client’s expectations. We take satisfaction in showing our customers how their project is been done so that they may appreciate the workmanship that goes into their project.

As a Landscape Contractor and Designer....
Our Goal… To exceed the expectations of every client by doing our work with Honesty, Quality, and Professionalism.                                  
Our approach… We first listen to what our clients want and make suggestions based on that and our experience. We then proceed to work in an efficient and flexible manner through every phase of the project to suit the client's needs.
 
We are happy to provide you with the following services and more:
Patios, walkways, steps, porches, verandas, pergolas, driveways, flower beds, gardens, planting, sprinklers, lighting, stone BBQs, stone fireplaces, and much more.

Letter from Danilo Otero, owner of Royal Town Landscape Development, March 2012:

Dear Customers,

I would like to thank you and congratulate you for helping children in Nicaragua go to school. Because of you, we were able to provide school supplies to 100 kids this past month and we are already working to provide another one hundred sets of school supplies this Summer. 

Thank You!  You made a big difference.

Regards,

Danilo

Our mission is to enhance lifestyles by providing aesthetically appealing home and property improvements with professional care and quality. Hardscape Interlock Design thrives to being nationally recognized as revolutionizing the paving and outdoor lifestyle industry by becoming the preferred choice. We are deeply committed to maintaining the industry’s highest standards of customer service and support. We listen to our customer needs and strive everyday to earn the credibility that has been associated with our company name and operations since we began.
Whether you’re looking for high-quality, durable driveways or planning to design an outdoor retreat with interlocking paving stones, choose Hardscapes Specialists to do the job. While being recognized for our high quality of work, Hardscapes is committed to providing you with great customer service. Our experts look to cut no corners and are determined to not only meet, but exceed your all expectations. With our dynamic designs and superior customer service, we are certain that you’ll be ecstatic with the outcome of the project

Having a hard time constructing a unique design for your home? Not a problem- Hardscapes Sales representatives have between 5-10 years of skilled and creative installation experience in the industry. They are also trained to help you construct exceptional quality and aesthetically beautiful designs to meet all your outdoor desires. If your still having trouble envisioning the outcome of your project, Hardscapes also offers a rendered design of your home to help you reach beyond your imagination and help visualize the final product. At Hardscapes, we have the experience and the knowledge to take your vision and make it into a reality. We plan on making your home the talk of the neighbourhood!
Hardscapes takes pride on our quality of work, while also being respectful to your neighbours by maintaining a clean and hazard free environment for the duration of the job. We guarantee that you will work with the same employees to oversee your project from concepts to its completion. Our paving stone installers are professional, respectful, fast and reliable. While many of our competitors leave projects incomplete and return to them at a later date, we are committed to concentrating on your job from start to finish, before moving onto another project. We are a design company full of innovative ideas and dedicated staff.

Patios, walkways, steps, porches, verandas, pergolas, driveways, flower beds, gardens, planting, sprinklers, lighting, stone BBQs, stone fireplaces, and much more.

Letter from Danilo Otero, owner of Royal Town Landscape Development, March 2012:

Dear Customers,

I would like to thank you and congratulate you for helping children in Nicaragua go to school. Because of you, we were able to provide school supplies to 100 kids this past month and we are already working to provide another one hundred sets of school supplies this Summer. 

Thank You!  You made a big difference.

Regards,

Danilo

profile:
Ontario Green Irrigation is the company to service your irrigation needs in the GTA and the surrounding areas. Our mission is to beautify residential properties through quality lawn and shrub irrigation.
At Ontario Green Irrigation, we take pride in serving our customers. It's our desire to exceed your expectations in every way. We’d love to hear from you anytime. Contact us by phone or complete our online form and someone will be in touch with you to answer any questions or hear any suggestions you might have. 
We build irrigation systems that conserve water and automate the process of caring for lawns. Very little needs to be done on the part of our clients to achieve a healthy landscape. We coordinate with the town, take all necessary measurements and arrange for a licensed plumber to complete the hook-up with your plumbing system. Our state of the art equipment allows us to be efficient and available at all times. It also allows us to spend more time getting to know the needs of each particular lawn and customize the system accordingly.  
We are trained and experienced professional irrigation contractors with a history of customer satisfaction in both system installation and service We will select the right Rain Bird products for the unique needs of your landscape, program your controlled to operate at maximum efficiency, and instruct you on how to adjust your system's watering schedule to meet seasonal requirements.
service_area: Brampton, Mississauga, Etobicoke, North York, King City, Nobleton, Gormley, Markham, Vaughan, Toronto, GTA,
products:
We carry full lines of the most popular and good qualtiy sprinkler brands of Rotors, Spray heads, Electric Valves, Controllers, Drip Irrigation, Rain Sensors, etc. As a Rainbird Select Contractor we will install quality irrigation systems with genuine Rain Bird products.
Ontario Green Irrigation proudly uses almost exclusively Hunter and Rainbird Irrigation Products. Hunter and Rainbird products are known as the "Cadillac" of the industry and include a complete lines of sprinklers, rotary heads, shrub heads, valves, controllers (timers) and a variety of accessory products, including rain sensors. Many Hunter and Rainbird products are guaranteed for up to 5 years and can be replaced for labor costs only in the event of failure.
Rotary Sprinkler Rotor-type sprinklers have one or more moving streams of water that rotate around the sprinkler head.
Spray Sprinkler Spray-type sprinklers spray a fan of water out of the nozzle, similar to a shower head.
Valves Electric solenoid valves used for turning on irrigation circuits (sprinklers or drip emitters.) Includes anti-siphon, angle, and globe type valves.
Controllers Controllers are fancy timers used to turn on and off automatic valves.
services:
REPAIR ALL BRANDS OF LAWN SPRINKLERS QUICKLY AND PROPERLY.
Our service techs are experienced and well-trained, and our service trucks are equipped with the latest troubleshooting equipment which allows us to quickly diagnose, troubleshoot, and properly repair all brands of sprinkler systems.
RE-ROUTING A SPRINKLER SYSTEM during swimming pool construction is no problem for Fellows Irrigation. We will cap off existing irrigation to permit usage of lawn sprinklers in areas not affected by construction, then re-route sprinklers around pool as needed to maintain a beautiful backyard.
INSTALL NEW LAWN SPRINKLERS SYSTEM - Ontario Green Irrigation will custom-design and install your system to give the most efficient, cost effective lawn sprinkler possible. Zone landscape areas to water according to watering needs. Landscape areas in full shade (between houses, for example) need less water than full sun areas. Proper zoning of your system will cost more to install but save you money in the future as well as save our most precious resource - water!
QUALITY PRODUCTS COMBINED WITH SKILLED SERVICE TECHS is what Ontario Green Irrigation is about and what will make you a satisfied customer.

profile:
VP Landscape is more than just a company, it is years built on hard work, dedication and passion for the industry. In his younger years, owner, Vito lived in Sala Consilina in the province of Salerno, in Italy. In a town where agriculture and farming was a main source of income, Vito was always intrigued by landscaping. When he immigrated to Canada he began his journey in landscape where he worked alongside his brothers. VP Landscape was born when Vito decided it was time to chase his dreams and begin his very own landscaping company.

Today, you will see VP Landscape and their work in high-end, residential properties in and around the GTA. Vito, alongside his son, Michael work together to envision and then execute the unique designs that they imagine for each individual client. They pride themselves on their ability to respect client privacy during and upon completion of every project. Their speciality remains in formal and manicured properties in which their expertise and passion evidently shine through.

Many of the details that you see in their work have been inspired by gardens and landscapes all over the world. Their various style adaptability, outstanding attention to detail and family orientated nature makes them one of the most reputable and personable landscape companies in Canada.

profile:
Welcome to Simply Exquisite, we are a construction and renovations general contractor in Toronto, serving the GTA and surrounding areas.

For over 20 years we have worked with property and homeowners providing them with high caliber commercial and home renovation services. We have earned our reputation as one of the best general contractors in the GTA through our trade expertise and professionalism. We are customer-service driven, pay extra attention to details, and deliver a quality product, on time and budget.

We approach every project with this simply promise: Every home renovation, general contracting, and construction project will be Simply Exquisite. That is our guarantee.

Whether you are looking to do a home renovation in Toronto, from kitchen design and renovations, to bathroom remodels and basement finishing, or something smaller like having your kitchen refaced or installing basement heated flooring, you can trust the best construction company in Toronto to give you the peace of mind of a job well done.

We offer award-winning renovation services that come with a 5-year warranty. We provide in-house design services and counseling, free of charge, with a licensed architectural designer. We extend this added value with every one of our projects so that you can be sure that your project will satisfy your needs.

Established in 2004, 51 Construction Ltd. has devoted to providing the highest, safest, most professional and customized construction and renovation services for our clients. profile:
Aventus Landscaping is a premier award winning residential landscape construction firm that has been servicing the Toronto and Greater Toronto communities since 2010.  We are a complete landscape design and build company specializing in outdoor living spaces with the simple objective of beautifying the neighbourhoods we work in. 

We have a hands-on approach to our project deliverables as we personally oversee every project detail ensuring our outcome meets our gold standard of quality.  After all:  your  goal is our goal – to design and build a dream landscaping project be it for functionality or entertainment purposes our commitment to excellence remains the same.  

Our landscape designers take pride in finding creative and unique approaches to landscaping that not only beautify your property, but do so in a cost efficient way. Whether your intentions are to create a ‘staycation’ escape, a more comfortable outdoor entertaining area or a low maintenance approach to help keep up with your busy lifestyle our team will work with you by understanding your needs and creating a personalized landscape design that accommodates. 

We are always looking forward to servicing new clients.

Since 1991 Mark has been honing his skills working with natural stone in a landscaping setting. Mark's traditional approach to flagstone patios and walkways, steps and retaining walls means that the tools of choice are chisel and hammer.

This means a dramatic reduction in noise and stone-dust when compared to saw heavy work, but it also means a deeper understanding of the quality and nature of stone and of the character of the space it is designed to inhabit.

profile:
Toronto Landscaping Contractor

Merlin Landscape Construction is an outdoor design and build landscape contracting company in Toronto. Believing that form follows function our team of landscape professionals applies real world knowledge to each project.

Designed to Fit

One of our top priorities is to educate our clients. Industry standard installation procedures and proper material selection are paramount to any successful landscape renovation.

Landscaping Tip:

Possibly one of the most prevalent mistakes homeowners make is to take on their landscape a little at a time. They start projects, begin to clear areas add a mix of plants and continue without a plan. The outcome is a mishmash of plantings and gardens that give the property a disorganized feel. Implementing a design plan with a prepared budget will lead a homeowner to a beautiful landscape that they can feel good about.

Get in touch with Merlin Landscape Construction today to start your landscape plan. Visit Online @ MerlinConstruction.ca or Call 416 880 0151 or 647-328-9840

Since the spring of 2000, Simple Solutions Landscaping has been offering quality services year-round in the North York neighborhoods of Armour Heights, Bathurst Manor, Clanton Park, Bayview Village, Newtonbrook, and Willowdale. We are dedicated to treating our clients with friendly and personalized customer service.

Brian Withey of Simple Solutions Landscaping is an established North York, and Toronto based landscaping company. They offer quality services year-round, with a focus on customer service. 

Since 2000, we've been helping people like you to maintain and enjoy the outside of your property.

Whether you are looking for general landscaping services or a company that can handle sodding, lawn aerating, grass cutting, hedge trimming, seeding, lawn dethachment or other property maintenance jobs, Simple Solutions has got you covered.

We improve the value of your property by caring for your yard. A new garden or walkway improves the curb appeal of your home. We create custom plans to suit your needs.

In the winter, we are on call 24/7 to remove snow from your drive and walkways with an easy fixed monthly bill. We use quality snow removal equipment to clear the path so you can feel safe and relaxed all winter long.

Simple Solutions is dedicated to ensuring you're satisfied with the job, we welcome your phone calls and questions. Call us today for help with your landscaping or snow removal needs!

profile:
We recommend the use of a professional landscape contractor for your project. You are making an important investment in your home. Don’t let poor workmanship turn your ideal plan into a disappointment. Proper site preparation with correct grading, base material and compaction is key to ensuring your new outdoor space (patio, driveway, walkway, etc.) looks great and stays even and safe for years to come.

****

Hiring the right landscape contractor to install your project can be a daunting task. Even if you have done this before or are experienced in hiring contractors for other projects around the home, hiring a landscape contractor has some additional unique challenges. Landscaping includes all the aspects of design, installation, and in most cases, horticulture.

****

The contractor you hire should have technical, business and interpersonal skills, as well as the tools and the experience needed to complete your paving stone and/or retaining wall project. Finding contractors who are experienced in installing landscape projects similar to yours, is one of the best ways to narrow down your final selection. These contractors will know what materials and techniques are needed for your landscape installation and will most likely have the labor and equipment to do it right.

GMCC Ltd. has been a locally owned and managed company providing landscaping and snow removal services in Toronto and surrounding areas. During this period, we have successfully served a diverse set of client segments that include corporate, Government, private businesses, industrial, retail, residential and condominiums.

Our stability, working for you

We're proudly Canadian. Our roots are in Toronto and we're here for the long haul. And we take pride in delivering our services to Toronto's business community... now and in the future.

Our finest assets - People, commitment and technology!

Our most important resource is our people. After all, they're the ones that ensure your premises are clean and healthy. Our success hinges on providing highly trained staff and a dedicated, experienced management team to lead them.

We're constantly seeking out new products and technologies to improve performance and decrease costs (that are then passed on to you).

profile:
DURABASE INTERLOCKING & LANDSCAPING
Services
Our experienced crew specializes in hardscaping and outdoor living construction projects. We work closely with our customers to create the complete property of your dreams. DURABASE Interlocking & Landscaping has a long-standing reputation of providing durable, dependable, quality service and excellent customer satisfaction. We will work for you to create an atmosphere that is entertaining and inviting, your wish list and your budget carefully weighting all available options:
Retaining Walls & Stair Systems
Decks, Fences & Gazebos
Landscaping Design & Build
Grading, Sodding, Planting, & Brickler
Waterfalls & Landscaping Lighting
Stone Masonry, Concrete Work & Irrigation
Flagstone (Porch Resurfacing) & Natural Stone
Interlocking Driveways, Walkways, Patios & Pool Landscaping…
BACKYARD & PATIOS
Transform these spaces and outdoor living areas with beautiful and functional designs that you will be proud of and will want to share with your family and friends. Each project begins by listening to your desires and preferences while being aware of your budget. We offer suggestions and solutions to achieve your outdoor living goals.
Our patios are functional and are built from only the finest materials, every patio is installed by our expert team.
DRIVEWAYS & WALKWAYS
As a homeowner you pride yourself on having a beautiful home, our goals are to make your dreams become a reality. We would love the opportunity to provide you with our superior quality and workmanship that meets and exceeds all expectations. With the proper installation of paving stones we will prevent pavers from cracking, shifting or separating. Your freshly installed pavers will look fantastic for generations.
With a wide range of sizes, shapes, colors, textures and patterns of pavers available to choose from, it makes customized design possible for every type of courtyard, patio, deck, driveway or walkway. You can be confident of the quality and durability of the pavers you need with DURABASE Inc.
TAKE YOUR STEPS to a new level!
With DURABASE Interlocking, Landscaping, we make sure that first impression when visitors step on to your property is a positive one.
Whether you are building a raised patio, rebuilding your front porch or building a walkway through an uneven yard, the addition of inclusion of beautiful stone, textured concrete or stone veneer steps will add beauty as well as practicality to your home, garden and yard.
DURABASE Interlock, Landscaping is the company that will fulfill your needs from design to build; from start-to-finish all work is completed by trained professionals. We offer prompt and courteous services and guarantee our craftsmanship on hardscapes. The success and exponential growth of the company traces back to OUR TEAM’s mandatory requirement for all jobs and his own personal motto “Provide quality, durable construction, and do it right the first time.”
DURABASE Interlock, Landscaping is extremely proud of its extensive list of glowing referrals and repeat clients, a tribute to both the quality of work and the employees who provide it.
Why Choose DURABASE Interlock, Landscaping?
DURABASE Interlock, Landscaping has a long-standing reputation of providing durable, dependable, quality service, craftsmanship and excellent customer satisfaction. We are locally owned and operated with friendly and professional management team and workforce.
CONTACT US:
805 Wilson Ave, #105
Toronto, Ontario, M3K 1E4

6476793816

profile:
The Backyard Urban Farm Company: Your Vegetable Garden Specialists. 
The Backyard Urban Farm Company is an award winning, family-run, organic vegetable landscaping company that designs, installs, plants and maintains edible gardens for residential and commercial clients throughout Toronto. Our mission is to ignite people’s passion for growing their own food and to help them reconnect with nature.

BUFCO is dedicated to participating in a worldwide food movement that encourages lowering our carbon footprint and trying to live more sustainably, naturally, independently, and locally.  We bring new opportunities for corporate and nuclear families, as well as individuals, to learn, teach, relax, share, play in, and eat from their own gardens. We believe that by tending our garden, we feed our minds, bodies, and souls, and contribute to the greater good.

profile:
M&S landscape design and build company  is a full service landscape company based in Toronto, serving Toronto and all of the GTA. We have been in the business for over 15 year's. We are not just a landscape design and build company, we are much more than that, we share your dreams, aspirations, wants and needs, surrounding your lovely nest you so adorably call home. We work on materializing your dreams, with empathy, understanding, love and above all dedication. All this is made possible through our long experience in the industry with most competent people onboard with us.

We specialize in natural stone & custom build interlocks, custom build fences, gates, gazebos and sheds, pergolas, swimming pools and much more in creating your dream garden. We also specialize in providing landscaping design 2d & 3d views for better understanding of your front yard or backyard spaces and we also execution of projects of all sizes.

We believe in delivering Quality and exceptional work and that makes us unique.

Feel free to contact us now on (647) 460-6782 to book a  FREE consultation and an estimate.
You can also email us on info@mnslandscaping.ca for work related queries.
